---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Work | Amid the Noise">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Work</h1>
    <p>
      Selected systems work focused on decision-making, trust, and real-world constraints.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <article>
      <h2>Case Studies</h2>
      <p>
        This section is being built to document applied work across product design, complex systems,
        and regulated environments. It will focus on how problems were framed, what decisions were
        made, and what changed as a result.
      </p>
      <p>
        The goal is not to recreate a résumé. It is to show how design thinking translates into
        operational clarity inside real systems.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <article>
      <h2>In Progress</h2>
      <p>
        The first case study is currently in development and will be published here shortly.
      </p>
      <p>
        Initial entries will focus on work involving trust, decision support, user experience in
        constrained environments, and systems where ambiguity carries real cost.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>